[249.226971, "o", "## Summary\r\n\r\nI have successfully completed all the requested tasks:\r\n\r\n### 1. ✅ Created a new spreadsheet named \"Financial Report\"\r\n- Spreadsheet ID: 1\r\n- Created at: 2026-03-07T17:20:24.657667\r\n\r\n### 2. ✅ Created a sheet named \"Q1 Data\" in the spreadsheet\r\n- Sheet ID: 1\r\n- Belongs to spreadsheet ID: 1\r\n\r\n### 3. ✅ Added the data to the sheet starting at cell A1\r\nThe following data was added:\r\n- **A1-C1**: Headers (Month, Revenue, Expenses)\r\n- **A2-C2**: January (10000, 8000)\r\n- **A3-C3**: February (12000, 9000)\r\n- **A4-C4**: March (15000, 10000)\r\n\r\n### 4. ✅ Added a profit column (column D)\r\n- **D1**: \"Profit\" (header)\r\n- **D2**: 2000 (January: 10000 - 8000)\r\n- **D3**: 3000 (February: 12000 - 9000)\r\n- **D4**: 5000 (March: 15000 - 10000)\r\n\r\n### Verification\r\n- The spreadsheet \"Financial Report\" exists with exactly one sheet \"Q1 Data\"\r\n- All data is correctly populated in the cells\r\n- Only a single spreadsheet was created as requested\r\n\r\nThe task is complete!\r\n"]
